im new to this and having a hard time downloading the songs on itunes will someone help?

to put a file on itunes, go to file-add file to library.Then go to the place where you downloaded the file,click the song at the top,then go to the bottom song and hold shift and click it.This selects all the songs in the folder.The you click on add file to library,and it should be on itunes
